long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension removes unnecessary elements from the page before printing.

Currently supported are only united.com and gmail.

To use - click on the icon and press Print button, that will hide unnecessary elements.
